link.message: Unable to get attribute value for projectInfo.url Please make sure you defined projectInfo.url in either forrest.properties.xml in $PROJECT_HOME or in the default.forrest.properties.xml of the plugin that is requesting this property. If you see this message, then most of the time you have spotted a plugin bug (i.e. forgot to define the plugin's default property). Please report to our mailing list.
